msgid "Redstone Lamp"
msgstr "Harrigorri lanpara"

msgid "Glows when powered by redstone power"
msgstr "Dir-dir egiten du harrigorri bidez aktibatzen denean"

msgid "Redstone lamps are simple redstone components which glow brightly (light level @1) when they receive redstone power."
msgstr ""
"Harrigorri lanparak harrigorri energia jasotzen dutenean distira handia (@1 "
"argi maila) egiten duten harrigorri osagai sinpleak dira."
